# Machine-private memory layer (Sabag360 principle 2, layer 3) — never committed
CLAUDE.local.md
**/CLAUDE.local.md

# Secrets — never commit real credentials
.env
**/.env
*.token
**/*.token
*.key
*.pem
secrets.*
**/secrets.*

# Runtime state (may contain chat_id / live tokens)
state.json
**/state.json
mirror_state.json
**/mirror_state.json
*.state
**/*.state
heartbeat.txt
**/heartbeat.txt
*.lock
**/*.lock

# Backups (may contain old secrets)
*.bak
*.bak-*
**/*.bak
**/*.bak-*

# Logs
*.log
**/*.log
logs/
**/logs/

# Python
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
venv/
**/venv/
.venv/
**/.venv/

# Media / runtime working folders (voice recordings, uploads)
*.m4a
*.oga
*.mp3
*.wav
inbox/
**/inbox/
processed/
**/processed/
failed/
**/failed/
tmp/
**/tmp/
